title: 820-00928 and 820-00281 No USB activity and PPVCC_S0_CPU never drops voltage
message: Clean boards all voltages are present including PPVCC_S0_CPU but that voltage never changes and there is no USB activity, on a good board PPVCC_S0_CPU drops from either 0.9V to 0.6V on the 00281 boards and drops from 1.1V to 0.7V on the 00928 boards, I will like to find out what to check on this boards before giving them back to customers, I know this CPUs fail a lot and will like to make sure for sure that the CPU is dead.
